				<article class="article-content">
					<h2 class="light-header">Extreme temperature: Iran city sizzles with  near world record-breaking heat of 165°F</h2>
										<div class="by-line">
										<a class="auther"  href="/reporter/andre-mitchell">						<span class="auther-name">Andre Mitchell</span>
					</a>
					<span class="auther-title"></span>
					 
					
					<time datetime="Sat, 01 Aug 2015 22:56:00 +0100" pubdate>01 August 2015</time></div>
					<div class="sharing-group">
